	These delightful dewberry maximum strength scented granules are for use in all oil burners. The lovely truly fresh and fruity aroma will quickly fill the room while the granules simmer away. The granules are packed in large amber glass jars that hold 130g of this wonderful product. The amber jar prolongs the aroma and colour&nbsp;and prevents&nbsp;worry about splitting plastic bags. To use simply place one or more teaspoons into the well of your burner and light the candle underneath &ndash; no need to add water. The granules then heat and will simmer away slowly releasing a wonderful and long lasting aroma that will fill your room. After use, just shake the used and cooled granules into a bin and replenish as needed. Why not check out our range of fantastic oil burners?</p>
